creator: TAIYO YUDEN
descriptionHtml:
Taiyo Yuden's piezoelectric pressure wave sensor module AYAP 05 can be connected to the Android terminal via USB cable or Bluetooth Low Energy.
Pulse rate, blood vessel age can be measured in real time.
Measurement data can be saved as a CSV file in the terminal.
You can display graphs of various data over time.
When you tap the [HELP] tab in the application, the instruction manual is displayed.
descriptionShort: This APP. can measure pulse waves using TAIYO YUDEN's sensor module AYAP 05.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
When the data measured by [Pulse wave display] is displayed on the [Psychoanalyzer], the rising edge of the graph is not displayed in the LLE and AB graph observation modes.
After displaying the data measured with [Pulse wave display] with [Psychoanalyzer], the graph can be displayed even if it returns to the [Pulse wave display] tab again.
